* Subfamily [[Discolepinae|Discolepinae]] {{small|Schileyko, 2006}}
** Genus ''[[Discolepis|Discolepis]]'' {{small|Ancey, 1904}}
* Subfamily [[Lucerninae|Lucerninae]] {{small|Swainson, 1840}}
** Genus ''[[Dentellaria|Dentellaria]]'' {{small|Schumacher, 1817}}
** Genus ''[[Eurycratera|Eurycratera]]'' {{small|H. Beck, 1837}}
*** == ''[[Leiocheila|Leiocheila]]'' {{small|Albers, 1850}}
*** == ''[[Leiostoma|Leiostoma]]'' {{small|Swainson, 1840}}
** Genus ''[[Lucerna|Lucerna]]'' {{small|Swainson, 1840}}
** Genus ''[[Thelidomus|Thelidomus]]'' {{small|Swainson, 1840}}
*** == ''[[Dendrocochlis|Dendrocochlis]]'' {{small|Pilsbry & A.P. Brown, 1910}}
*** == ''Pachystoma'' {{small|Albers, 1850}}
* [[高腰蝸牛亞科|高腰蝸牛亞科]] [[Pleurodontinae|Pleurodontinae]] {{small|Ihering, 1912}}
** Genus ''[[Gonostomopsis|Gonostomopsis]]'' {{small|Pilsbry, 1889}}
*** == ''[[Chrysodon|Chrysodon]]'' {{small|Ancey, 1887}}
